node.text:
I thought I'd do a photo d*mp today but I hate the word d*mp so I am calling this "Lindsey's photo assortment!" Lmao. 

The last few months I've covered SO much ground. I've been acting, glamour modeling, working out, designing my home with @sarahwestinteriors and per usual- loving on my little Tosh! (Still VERY single still so I've had a lot of time for ME) :) 

As Instagram continues to change I'm going to change with it! I am in the process of creating season 4 of my podcast EYES UP HERE. The long version of every show will be available and you're going to LOVE what I have planned. 🎧 

I also go LIVE every week on my Facebook Page and on my OF. My fan page is my personal interactive magazine. I love it and I put so much into it! 😍

*My Snapchat-I treat like my new Instagram stories. I post my days thoughtout. 
*My tik tok-I am still 🗑 and leaning into it! 
*My Twitter- Will always be my #1 baby. I am addicted to Twitter. 

Let me know how you like this photo assortment, what you want to see and also how cute Tosh is ( I love to hear it) Have the best Monday! 

Pictured: Miami, Cabo, Nevada, New Orleans, Hollywood, Big Bear :) 🌴 

Btw: most of these aren't edited 😛 #travel #interiordesign #dogsofinstagram
